Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.23,0:22:24.07,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}與你共度的時光  我很是留戀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.41,0:22:26.75,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}啊～ 從今以後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:34.29,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}許多看似平凡却又珍貴的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:37.97,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}讓我們一同創造
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.99,0:22:39.24,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs22}sun shiny day !
