Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  希爾維
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  難為你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疏忽了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈爾特曼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾維  大家就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去救夏露
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏露  夏露
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸出手後又會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會使自己地獄般的生活變得更淒慘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的那些話不過是站在富家子弟立場上的廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…
